              "cover_url": "https://p3-sign.douyinpic.com/tos-cn-i-dy/0777fce705ad412abfcc7528dfd83764~tplv-dy-resize-walign:360:q75.jpeg?lk3s=138a59ce&x-expires=1774756800&x-signature=QMEmhY6Sb4wuzTO9wytp3f%2FDrEY%3D&from=327834062&s=PackSourceEnum_PUBLISH&se=false&sc=cover&biz_tag=aweme_video&l=202603151236291771C55C29261BF89B08",
              "script": "名词复数变化多，一个口诀帮你掌握。\n\n名词复数有规律，一般词尾加s，如cat变为cats。\n\ns, x, ch, sh它们四个不规矩，词尾有它es，如bus变为buses，box变为boxes，watch变为watches，dish变为dishes。\n\n辅音字母加y结尾，把y变i加es，如baby变为babies，city变为cities。\n\nf, fe真小气，字母v来把它替，es在后别忘记，如leaf变为leaves，knife变为knives。\n\n字母o也很神奇，有生命的加es，没有生命就加s，如potato变为potatoes，photo变为photos。\n\n你都学会了吗？学会了给老师一颗小星星吧。"
