              "cover_url": "https://p3-sign.douyinpic.com/tos-cn-i-0813c000-ce/ogF5WL6BIgFQgTsOAgevwAvA7Ay5QG8rJAeeEw~tplv-dy-resize-walign:360:q75.jpeg?lk3s=138a59ce&x-expires=1774753200&x-signature=35goPjq4KRAMG5Wb91oYOGusxAo%3D&from=327834062&s=PackSourceEnum_PUBLISH&se=false&sc=cover&biz_tag=aweme_video&l=20260315114302F5F36B400CB12AE856E5",
              "script": "和雪莉老师来读经典的英文绘本故事。Today we're going to read When I Grow Up. So when you grow up, who do you want to be? Let's take a look.\n\nWhen I grow up, I want to be a pilot. What is a pilot? Tara, look at me. I can be a pilot. I can fly a plane up there in the sky too. That's so cool.\n\nOr I can be a shopkeeper. I will own a shop full of candies like this. Different kinds of candies. Wow, they're so sweet. Look at these yummy, yummy lollipops. So do you want to be a shopkeeper?\n\nOr I want to be a superhero. Look at me. I can be a superhero. I can lift up a car. I'm really strong. I have the superpower.\n\nOr I can be an artist. What can artists do? I can draw pictures. Look at me. I am an artist. I'm wearing a hat, and I can draw and paint pictures.\n\nI also can be a tennis player. I can play tennis with my friend. So do you want to be a tennis player? Do you want to be a tennis player or a football player or a basketball player?\n\nOr I want to be a pirate. What can a pirate do? I can sail my boat and go to the island to find the treasure box. Look at me. I am a pirate.\n\nOr I can be a zookeeper. I can keep a zoo, and I can see many, many different kinds of animals. Look at them, and we can be good friends. So do you want to be a zookeeper or an astronaut? An astronaut can fly up to outer space, walking on the moon. So do you want to be an astronaut?\n\nOr I can be a clown. I can juggle the balls. That's so much fun. Look at me. I am a clown.\n\nOr I want to be a scientist. This is a scientist. A scientist can do experiments. A, B, C, boom. Oh, do you want to be a scientist?\n\nOr I want to be a film star. I can stand on the stage performing for everyone and they will say, \"Bravo, good job.\" I want to be a famous movie star.\n\nSo who do you want to be when you grow up? Okay, so that's it for today."
