              "script": "只要五分钟，英语启蒙很轻松，和雪玲老师一起来读经典的英文故事吧。Today we're going to read, dear. 原来呀有一位小宝贝想要养一只宠物，所以呢他就给动物园写信。那么动物园会给他喜欢的宠物吗？好的，我们一起来看故事。\n\nDear zoo, 亲爱的动物园，one day I wrote to the zoo to send me a pet. Could you give me an animal? So they sent me an elephant. Wow, he was so big, right? The elephant was so big I couldn't keep it as my pet. So no. And I sent him back.\n\nNext one. So they sent me a giraffe. Wow, a tall, tall giraffe. He was too tall, I couldn't keep it as my pet. So no, I sent him back.\n\nSo they sent me a, what animal is inside? Let's open it up raw. What is it? A lion. He was so fierce. No, I sent him back.\n\nAnd then they sent me, sent me a camel. The camel was too grumpy. He was too grumpy. I couldn't keep the camel as my pet. So I sent him back.\n\nSo they sent me a, what animal is it inside? A snake. He was too scary. No, no, no. Take him back. No, I send him back to the zoo. I don't like it.\n\nSo they sent me a monkey. Monkey. But the monkey was so naughty. Jump over here. Jump over there. I don't like it. Let's send him back. I send him back.\n\nThen the zoo thought very, very hard, so they sent me a, what is it? Frog? Jumpy. Jumpy frog. He was too jumpy. I don't like it. I sent him back.\n\nAnd the zoo thought very, very, very hard this time, and they thought and thought and thought. So they sent me a. A puppy. Wow, a cute, cute, cute little puppy. I love it. He was perfect, and I kept the puppy as my pet.\n\nOkay, so that's all about dear zoo. 想跟雪玲老师来听更多经典的英文绘本故事，都可以来我的直播间和我一起来学。"
